snippet.title: PAYDAY 2: Legacy Collection
snippet.description: PAYDAY 2: Legacy Collection will provide many hours of intense and exciting action. The content in this pack includes a plethora of heists, characters, weapons, mods, and cosmetic items, for an ever richer PAYDAY 2 experience.
